1 equal the difference between:
2 “(a) Any amounts available as the free reimbursement rate established
3 by the United States Department of Agriculture for reimbursable meals; and
4 “(b) Any amounts otherwise reimbursed or paid by state, federal or other
5 sources.
6 “(4) The State Board of Education may adopt any rules necessary for
7 making reimbursements under this section.”.
